import React from 'react'
import { Link } from "react-router-dom"
import SongOverview from './SongOverview'

function Home() {
    return (
        <>
        <nav>
            <Link to="./about">About</Link>
        </nav>
        <main>
            
        <SongOverview />
        </main>
        </>
    )
}

export default Home
